    @{b}EXAMPLE@{ub}
        "ZOOM" "30 40 400 300 2" "FAST"
        IF RC THEN SAY "Can't zoom:" ErrorText(RC2)
        ELSE SAY "Elapsed time:" RESULT

    @{b}BUGS@{ub}
        The STEPS-parameter has no effect.

